data.description: .Are you looking for a brick ranch home that offers an ample amount of space? This home is for you!  This home offers three bedrooms & two full baths with oak hardwood floors and sits on a corner lot! This home features a rather large two car garage, unfinished basement, and an added bonus space on the second level! The second level space could offer a mother-in-law suite, large bedroom or even as your very own man cave!!  Let's not forget about the fully fenced in back yard that is great for pets.  Here at this location you are in walking distance to Northwood High School as well as the Saltville Golf Course.  Give me a call and schedule your showing today! HOME Is Being Sold AS  IS WHERE IS! Home inspection is welcome for informational purposes Only! Buyers or Buyers agent to verify all information
